 authentic in contemporary culture--the foundation upon which modern film studies sits.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aDetective and mystery storiesxFilm adaptations. 0aDetective and mystery stories, AmericanxHistory and criticism. 0aFilm criticismzGreat BritainxHistoryy20th century. 0aFilm criticismzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aFilm noirxHistory and criticism. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh1 aMaltby, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertRutgers University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311068861040uhttps://doi.org/10.36019/978081355103640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780813551036423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780813551036/original  a978-3-11-068861-0  Rutgers University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK